<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3774368>
    dc:description "Appendix A. A list of descriptions of extant adult male Coccomorpha, mainly since Theron’s pioneering work of 1958. It is unlikely to be complete, and so please contact the author if you know of others." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3774368/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3774366>
    dc:description "FIGURE 94.?Pulvinaria dodonaeae Maskell. Macropterous male. (Coccidae). Where A=cranial apophysis and R=dermal reticulations on ocular sclerite." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://zenodo.org/record/3774366/files/figure.png" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3774354>
    dc:description "FIGURE 88. Akermes scrobiculatus (Maskell). Macropterous male. (Coccidae). Where R=dermal reticulations on ocular sclerite." ;
