    a fabio:Figure .

<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3774356>
    dc:description "FIGURE 89. Akermes pinguis (Maskell). Macropterous male.(Coccidae).Where K=procoxa showing coxal bristles and R=dermal reticulations on ocular sclerite." ;
