<http://dx.doi.org/10.5281/zenodo.3774352>
    dc:description "FIGURE 87. Parthenolecanium persicae (Fabricius). Macropterous male. (Coccidae). Where A=cranial apophysis, D=fleshy seta, E=hair-like seta, and R=dermal reticulations on ocular sclerite." ;
